INSERT INTO `scripts` VALUES (1,1,8,'Back then, the world was divided in two. Vicious predator or meek prev.','그때 세상은 두 부류로 나뉘었죠. 사악한 포식자와, 온순한 사냥감.',0,'Judy',0),(2,1,17,'But over time, we evolved, and moved beyond our primitive, savage ways.','하지만 우린 진화했고, 더는 원시적이고 야만적이지 않죠.',0,'Judy',9),(3,1,22,'Now, predator and prey live in harmony.','이젠 맹수와 먹잇감이 화목하게 살고,',0,'Judy',17),(4,1,27,'And every young mammal has multitudinous opportunities.','젊은 포유류들은 많은 기회를 갖게 됐어요.',0,'Judy',22),(5,1,30,'Yeah. I don\'t have to cower in a herd anymore.','맞아요. 전 더 이상 겁쟁이처럼 숨어 살 필요가 없죠.',0,'Sharla',27),(6,1,36,'Instead, I can be an astronaut.','전 커서 우주비행사가 될 거예요.',0,'Sharla',31),(7,1,40,'I don\'t have to be a lonely hunter anymore.','전 커서 고독한 사냥꾼이 아닌,',0,'Jaguar',37),(8,1,43,'Today, I can hunt for tax exemptions.','열심히 공부해서',0,'Jaguar',40),(9,1,46,'I\'m gonna be an actuary!','보험 전문가로 꼭 성공할래요!',0,'Jaguar',43),(10,1,50,'And I can make the world a better place.','전 더 좋은 세상을 만들 거예요.',0,'Judy',47),(11,1,56,'I am going to be … a police officer!','저는….경찰이 될거예요!',1,'Judy',51),(13,4,2,'Keep the change.','잔돈은 됐어요.',0,'Judy',0),(14,4,8,'Officer, I can\'t thank you enough. So kind, really. Can I pay you back?','경관님, 정말 고마워요. 참 친절하시네요. 돈은 꼭 갚을게요.',0,'Nick',3),(15,4,10,'Oh, no, my treat. It just…','아뇨, 됐어요 전 그냥..',0,'Judy',8),(16,4,13,'You know, it burns me up to see folk…with such backward attituds toward foxes…','여우에게 편견을 가진 동물들을 보면 화가 나요.',0,'Judy',10),(17,4,19,'I just wanna say you\'re a great dad and just a real articulate fela.','선생님은 정말 좋은 아빠이자..아주 멋진 남자세요.',0,'Judy',14),(18,4,21,'Oh, well that is high praise.','과찬이세요.',0,'Nick',19),(19,4,24,'It\'s rare that I find someone so non-patronizing.','요즘 보기 드문 분이시네요. 성함이..?',0,'Nick',22),(22,4,30,'And you, little guy…','그리고 우리 꼬마친구,, ',0,'Judy',29),(23,4,34,'You want to be an elephant when you grow up? You\'d be an elephant. ','커서 코끼리가 되고 싶어? 그렇다면 넌 코끼리가 될 수 있어.',0,'Judy',31),(24,4,39,'Because this is Zootopia. Anyone can be anything.','왜냐하면 여기 주토피아에선 누구나 뭐든지 될 수 있으니까.',0,'Judy',35),(25,4,43,'Oh, boy. I tell him that all the time','저도 늘 그렇게 말해줘요.',0,'Nick',40),(26,4,45,'All right, here you go. Two paws, Yeah.','자, 두 발로 받으렴, 그렇지.',0,'Nick',43),(27,4,48,'Oh, look at that smile. That\'s a \'happy birthday\' smile.','웃는 것 좀 보세요. 행복한 생일이 됐네요.',0,'Nick',45),(28,4,53,'All right, give her a little bye-bye toot-toot.','경찰관님께 \"뛰뛰\"\" 인사 해야지\"',1,'Nick',49),(29,13,7,'Mr. Manchas? Judy Hopps, ZPD','만차스씨? 주디 홉스 경관입니다.',0,'Judy',0),(30,13,10,'We just wanna know what happened to Emmitt Otterton.','에밋 오터톤에 대해 물어볼게 있어요.',0,'Judy',7),(31,13,20,'You..should be asking…what happened to me.','내가..왜 이렇게 됐는지..그걸 물어봐야지.',0,'Manchas',15),(32,13,25,'Whoa! Uh, a teensy otter did that?','헉! 그 작은 수달이 그런 거예요?',0,'Nick',20),(33,13,26,'What happened?','어떻게 된 거죠?',0,'Judy',25),(34,13,28,'He was an animal','녀석은 완전 짐승이었어',0,'Manchas',26),(35,13,33,'Down... on all fours.','미친듯이..난동을 부렸지.',0,'Manchas',30),(36,13,37,'He was a savage!','야수 그 자체였다고!',0,'Manchas',36),(37,13,50,'There was no warning.','그러고는 갑자기',0,'Manchas',48),(38,13,53,'He just kept yelling about the Night Howlers.','\"밤의 울음꾼\"\"에 대해 외쳐댔어\"',0,'Manchas',50),(39,13,56,'Over and over. The Night Howlers.','끊임없이 계속해서.',0,'Manchas',53),(40,13,61,'So, you know about the Night Howlers, too? Good. Good good.','그래서..밤의 울음꾼에 대해 아신다는 거군요? 좋습니다. 아주 좋아요.',0,'Nick',56),(41,13,66,'Because the Night Howlers.. Are exactly what we are here to talk about. Right?','왜냐하면 사실 그것때문에 찾아왔거든요. 그렇죠?',0,'Nick',61),(42,13,71,'Yep. So, up, so you just open the door.. And tell us what you know','맞아요. 그러니까 문 열고 아는대로 말씀해 주시면',0,'Judy',67),(43,13,75,'and we will tell you what we know. Okay?','저희도 아는 걸 말해드릴게요. 어때요?',1,'Judy',72),(44,2,2,'You don\'t scare me, Gideon.','난 너 하나도 안무서워, 기디온',0,'Judy',0),(45,2,4,'You scared now?','이제 무섭냐?',0,'Gideon',3),(46,2,7,'Look at her nose twitch. She is scared.','코 떨리는 것 봐, 완전 쫄았네',0,'Travis',5),(47,2,9,'Cry little baby bunny.','울어봐, 꼬마 토끼',0,'Gideon',7),(48,2,16,'Oh, you don\'t know when to quit, do you?','그만둘 줄을 모르는구나, 그럼 내가 알려주지.',0,'Gideon',13),(49,2,25,'I want you to remember this moment.','니가 이순간을 잊지 않길 바래',0,'Gideon',22),(50,2,31,'the next time you think…you will ever be anything more than just a stupid carrot-farming, dumb bunny.','다음부터는.. 니가 할 수 있는건 홍당무나 키우는 것 뿐이라는걸 명심해야 될 거야.',0,'Gideon',25),(51,2,37,'That looks bad.','아프겠다..',0,'Sheep1',36),(52,2,39,'Are you okay, Judy?','괜찮아 주디?',0,'Sheep2',37),(53,2,40,'Yeah. Yeah, I\'m okay.','응..난 괜찮아.',0,'Judy',39),(54,2,42,'Here you go.','자, 여기 받아.',0,'Judy',41),(55,2,45,'Wow! You got our tickets!','우와! 우리 표잖아!',0,'Sheep2',43),(56,2,47,'You\'re awesome, Judy!','너 정말 멋지다, 주디!',0,'Sheep1',45),(57,2,50,'Yeah, that Gideon Grey doesn\'t know what he\'s talking about.','그 기디온 녀석은 아무것도 몰라.',0,'Sheep2',47),(58,2,52,'Well, he was right about one thing.','그래도 걔 말중에 한 개는 맞았어.',0,'Judy',50),(59,2,57,'I don\'t know when to quit.','난 절대 그만두지 않아.',1,'Judy',54),(60,31,2,'Am I supposed to feel this ridiculous?','지금 황당한게 정상인 거죠?',0,'Kristoff',0),(61,31,4,'OH, yeah. Definitely.','그럼요, 당연하죠',0,'Ryder',3),(62,31,6,'Everyone ready?','다 준비됐지?',0,'Ryder',5),(63,31,12,'Wait. You talk for them, too?','잠깐, 당신도 순록이랑 대화해요?',0,'Kristoff',10),(64,31,13,'I do.','네',0,'Ryder',12),(65,31,14,'It\'s like you can actually hear what they\'re thinking.','걔들 생각이 들리는 것 같고?',0,'Kristoff',13),(66,31,17,'Yeah. And then you just say it.','네, 그리고 그게 말로 막 나와요.',0,'Ryder',15),(67,31,19,'And then you just say it.','말로 막 나오고요.',0,'Kristoff',17),(68,31,22,'Okay. Here she comes.','좋아, 그녀가 와요!',0,'Ryder',21),(69,31,27,'Princess Anna of Arendelle…','아렌델의 안나 공주님',0,'Kristoff',25),(70,31,31,'my feisty, fearless, ginger-sweet love.','당돌하고 용감한 빨강 머리 내 사랑',0,'Kristoff',27),(71,31,34,'Will you marry me?','저와 결혼해 주시겠어요?',0,'Kristoff',32),(72,31,40,'Um…no. The princess left with the queen.','음..아뇨. 공주님은 여왕님과 떠나셨습니다.',0,'Yelena',35),(73,31,41,'What? Wait, what? What?','네? 잠깐만, 뭐라고요?',0,'Kristoff',40),(74,31,45,'I wouldn\'t try to follow. Thery\'re long gone.','따라가긴 늦었어요. 떠난 지 꽤 됐거든요.',0,'Yelena',42),(75,31,46,'Long gone?','꽤 됐다고요?',0,'Kristoff',45),(76,31,53,'So yeah. Um, we\'re heading west to the Lichen Meadows.','네 그래요. 우린 서쪽, 라이칸 초원으로 갈 겁니다.',0,'Yelena',47),(77,31,54,'You can come with us if you want.','원한다면 같이 가시죠.',1,'Yelena',53),(78,26,2,'Come in.','들어와',0,'Elsa',0),(79,26,5,'Yep. Something\'s wrong.','그래. 문제가 있네.',0,'Anna',4),(80,26,6,'With you?','너한테?',0,'Elsa',5),(81,26,9,'No, with you. You\'re wearing Mother\'s scarf.','아니, 언니한테. 엄마 스카프를 두르고 있잖아.',0,'Anna',7),(82,26,11,'You do that when something\'s wrong.','뭔가 안 좋을 때 이러잖아.',0,'Anna',10),(83,26,13,'Did we hurt your feelings?','혹시 우리가 기분 상하게 했어?',0,'Anna',12),(84,26,15,'I\'m so sorry if we did.','그랬다면 미안해.',0,'Anna',14),(85,26,17,'You know, very few people are actually good at family games.','언니 말고도 가족 게임 못하는 사람 있어.',0,'Anna',15),(86,26,19,'That\'s just a fact.','정말로.',0,'Anna',18),(87,26,20,'No, that\'s not it.','아냐, 그런 거 아냐.',0,'Elsa',19),(88,26,22,'Then, what is it?','그럼 무슨일인데?',0,'Anna',21),(89,26,32,'I just don\'t wanna mess things up.','그냥.. 망치고 싶지 않아서 그래',0,'Elsa',30),(90,26,35,'What\'s things? You\'re doing great.','뭘 망쳐? 언니는 잘하고 있어.',0,'Anna',33),(91,26,40,'Oh, Elsa, when are you going to see yourslf the way I see you?','언니, 난 언니를 아는데 언니는 왜 스스로를 몰라?',0,'Anna',36),(92,26,44,'What would I do without you?','네가 없으면 어쩌지?',0,'Elsa',43),(93,26,46,'You\'ll always have me.','난 늘 곁에 있을 거야.',0,'Anna',45),(94,26,51,'I know what you need. Come on, come here.','이럴때 필요한게 뭔지 알지. 이리와 얼른!',0,'Anna',49),(95,26,55,'In Mama\'s words, \'cuddle close, scooch in.\'','엄마처럼 말하자면, \'이리로 와 누우렴.\'',1,'Anna',51),(96,3,0,'a','가',0,'Bonnie',0),(97,3,0,'a','가',0,'Stu',0),(98,3,0,'a','가',0,'Judy',0),(99,5,0,'a','가',0,'Judy',0),(100,5,0,'a','가',0,'Nick',0),(161,6,0,'a','가',0,'Benjamin',0),(102,6,0,'a','가',0,'Mrs. Otterton',0),(103,6,0,'a','가',0,'Bogo',0),(163,7,0,'a','가',0,'Benjamin',0),(165,9,0,'a','가',0,'Judy',0),(106,7,0,'a','가',0,'Mrs. Otterton',0),(107,7,0,'a','가',0,'Bogo',0),(164